                },
                {
                  "text": "Maria Smodics-Neumann , Dr. Christian Stocker , Cornelia Ecker , Dietmar Keck , Katharina Kucharowits , Rosa Ecker, MBA und Alois Kainz .",
                  "timeStart": "3.640",
                  "timeEnd": "7.120",
